# Module: tf.saved_model.builder



Defined in [`tensorflow/saved_model/builder/__init__.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.10/tensorflow/saved_model/builder/__init__.py).

SavedModel builder.

Builds a SavedModel that can be saved to storage, is language neutral, and
enables systems to produce, consume, or transform TensorFlow Models.

## Classes

[`class SavedModelBuilder`](../../tf/saved_model/builder/SavedModelBuilder): Builds the `SavedModel` protocol buffer and saves variables and assets.
